name: Silk Road 004
description:
SILK ROAD : An Exchange of ART , MUSIC & HEALING !!

Just Like the ancient trading route that linked the Western World with the Middle East and Asia, our SILK ROAD gathering is meant to be a beautiful exchange of what 3 companies, SPACE BRAINS, MYCORRHIZA & THE BOOM BOOM ROOM has brought to our community for many years now. Be a witness to the wonder and delight as we recreate our own version of the magic brought to you by the exchange of Immersive ART EXPERIENCES, BUMPIN BEATS AND HEALING VIBRATIONS. With all three collectives bringing the best they have to offer we will have hand-crafted goods by amazing vendors, live artists, flow artists, experience creators and many more wondrous surprises.

______
Photography by Sebuh Honarchian while attending Silk Road Mojave Desert Gathering 2021
